w:r.w:t: Fritzing Parts for Adventure Kit: 30 Days Lost
Fritzing is an open-source software designed for creating clean and professional wiring diagrams.
Visit fritzing.org and install the software.
Open Fritzing to find built-in components like buttons and LEDs.
Download the parts you’d like above.
Right-click the parts tab to import and use extra components.
